<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset='utf-8' />
        <title>Your Event Ticket</title>
        <style>
            .ticket-container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family:
            Arial, sans-serif; } .ticket { border: 2px solid #000;
            border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; background-color:
            #f8f8f8; } .event-details { margin: 15px 0; } .barcode { text-align:
            center; margin: 20px 0; } .barcode img { max-width: 300px; height:
            auto; } .ticket-info { font-size: 14px; color: #666; } .important {
            color: #d23; font-weight: bold; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class='ticket-container'>
            <h1>Your Event Ticket</h1>
            <p>Hello {{attendeeName}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering for
                {{eventName}}. Here's your ticket:</p>

            <div class='ticket'>
                <h2>{{eventName}}</h2>
                <div class='event-details'>
                    <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{eventTime}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Venue:</strong> {{venue}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Ticket Type:</strong> {{ticketType}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Ticket ID:</strong> {{ticketId}}</p>
                </div>

                <div class='barcode'>
                    <img src='{{cidForbarcodeUrl}}' alt='Ticket Barcode' />
                </div>

                <div class='ticket-info'>
                    <p class='important'>Important Notes:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Please arrive at least 30 minutes before the event</li>
                        <li>This ticket is unique and can only be used once</li>
                        <li>Please have a valid ID with you</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br />{{organizerName}}</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
